
Project 04
Sales Analysis using Python to evaluate retail sales performance, calculate KPIs, identify business trends, and visualize insights for decision-making.
Features
• Total Revenue
• Average Order Value (AOV)
• Top Products
• Top Regions
• Monthly Sales Trend
• Business Recommendations
Tools & Libraries
Python 3, Pandas, Matplotlib
Project Structure
sales_analysis.py – Main analysis script
README.docx – Project documentation
Output
The program generates KPI results in the console and displays charts for product performance, regional sales, and monthly sales trends.
Conclusion
The analysis highlights high-performing products and regions, enabling data-driven business decisions and improved sales strategies.

